# ü§ñ Chatbot Navigation & Help Guide - RAG Documentation

This document provides comprehensive navigation paths and detailed help instructions for the Bonyad app chatbot. It's structured in chunks optimized for RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) systems.

**IMPORTANT**: Each navigation instruction includes the actual SwiftUI view component name that should be rendered when clicked. Use these view names to programmatically navigate users to the correct screens.

