## üéØ SwiftUI View Component Reference

### Main Tab Views (User)

| Tab | View Component | Description |
|-----|---------------|-------------|
| Home | `HomeView(selectedTab: $selectedTab)` | Main user home screen |
| Profile | `ProfileView()` | User profile and settings |
| My Projects | `AllUserProjectsView()` | All user projects with filters |
| Appointments | `AppointmentsListView()` | User appointments list |
| Create Project | `CreateProjectSelectionView()` | Choose AI or Manual project creation |

### Main Tab Views (Service Provider)

| Tab | View Component | Description |
|-----|---------------|-------------|
| Home | `HomeContentView(geo: geo)` | Service provider home screen |
| Projects | `AvailableProjectsView()` | Available projects to bid on |
| Appointments | `AppointmentsListView()` | Service provider appointments |
| Payments | `CommissionPaymentView()` | Commission payments view |
| Profile | `ProfileView()` | Service provider profile |

### Navigation Destination Views

| Action | View Component | Parameters |
|--------|---------------|------------|
| View Service Providers | `ServiceProvidersView(selectedService: serviceCategory)` | Requires `selectedService` parameter |
| View All Services | `PickServiceView()` | No parameters |
| View Technician Profile | `TechUserProfileView(technicianId: Int)` | Requires `technicianId` |
| View Project Details | `ProjectStatusTimelineView(projectId: String, isServiceProvider: Bool)` | Requires `projectId`, optional `isServiceProvider` |
| Chat List | `ChatsModule.ListView()` | No parameters |
| View Projects List | `ProjectsListView(initialFilters: ProjectFilters)` | Requires `initialFilters` |
| Running Projects | `RunningProjectsView()` | No parameters |
| Completed Projects | `CompletedProjectsView()` | No parameters |
| My Offers | `MyOffersPage()` | No parameters |
| Bidded Projects | `BiddedProjectsView()` | No parameters |
| Accepted Offers | `AcceptedOffersView()` | No parameters |
| Technician Accepted Offers | `TechnicianAcceptedOffersView()` | No parameters |
| My Listings with Offers | `MyListingsWithOffersView()` | No parameters |

### Project Creation Views

| Step | View Component | Description |
|------|---------------|-------------|
| Selection | `CreateProjectSelectionView()` | Choose AI or Manual |
| AI Form | `ConversationalAIForm()` | AI-assisted project creation |
| Manual Form | `ManualProjectForm()` | Manual project entry form |
| Project Type | `ProjectTypeSelectionView()` | Select project type |

### Portfolio Views (Service Provider)

| Action | View Component | Description |
|--------|---------------|-------------|
| Create Portfolio | `CreatePortfolioView()` | Initial portfolio creation |
| Portfolio Management | `PortfolioManagementView()` | Manage existing portfolio |
| Add Past Project | `AddPastProjectView()` | Add past project to portfolio |
| Edit Past Project | `EditPastProjectView()` | Edit existing past project |
| Edit Portfolio | `EditPortfolioView()` | Edit portfolio details |

### Profile & Settings Views

| Action | View Component | Description |
|--------|---------------|-------------|
| My Profile | `MyProfileView()` | View/edit user profile |
| Technician Profile Management | `TechnicianProfileManagementView()` | Manage technician profile |
| Support Center | `SupportCenterView()` | Support tickets and help |

### Contract & Payment Views

| Action | View Component | Description |
|--------|---------------|-------------|
| Phase Approval | `PhaseApprovalView()` | Approve project phases |
| Contract Payment | `ContractPaymentView()` | Make phase payments |
| Phase Review | `PhaseReviewView()` | Review phase details |
| Project Owner Edit | `ProjectOwnerEditView()` | Edit project as owner |

### How to Use View Components

When chatbot provides navigation instructions, it should return:

1. **View Component Name**: The exact SwiftUI struct name
2. **Required Parameters**: Any parameters needed to initialize the view
3. **Navigation Method**: How to navigate (tab selection, NavigationLink, etc.)

**Example Response Format:**
```json
{
  "action": "navigate",
  "view": "ProjectStatusTimelineView",
  "parameters": {
    "projectId": "123",
    "isServiceProvider": false
  },
  "method": "NavigationLink",
  "description": "Tap the project card to view details"
}
```

### Programmatic Navigation Methods

#### Method 1: Tab Selection
For main tab views, set the `selectedTab` binding:
```swift
// User tabs
selectedTab = .home          // Shows HomeView
selectedTab = .profile       // Shows ProfileView
selectedTab = .myProjects    // Shows AllUserProjectsView
selectedTab = .appointments  // Shows AppointmentsListView
selectedTab = .createProject // Shows CreateProjectSelectionView

// Service Provider tabs
selectedTab = .home      // Shows HomeContentView
selectedTab = .projects  // Shows AvailableProjectsView
selectedTab = .payments  // Shows CommissionPaymentView
selectedTab = .profile   // Shows ProfileView
```

#### Method 2: NavigationLink
For nested views, use NavigationLink:
```swift
NavigationLink(destination: ProjectStatusTimelineView(projectId: "123", isServiceProvider: false)) {
    Text("View Project")
}

NavigationLink(destination: ServiceProvidersView(selectedService: serviceCategory)) {
    Text("View Providers")
}

NavigationLink(destination: TechUserProfileView(technicianId: 456)) {
    Text("View Profile")
}
```

#### Method 3: Sheet Presentation
For modal views:
```swift
.sheet(isPresented: $showView) {
    CreatePortfolioView()
}

.sheet(isPresented: $showBidForm) {
    BidForm(projectId: "123")
}
```

### View Component Quick Reference

| User Intent | View Component | Navigation Method | Parameters |
|------------|---------------|-------------------|------------|
| View Home | `HomeView(selectedTab: $selectedTab)` | Tab: `.home` | `selectedTab` binding |
| View Profile | `ProfileView()` | Tab: `.profile` | None |
| View Projects | `AllUserProjectsView()` | Tab: `.myProjects` | None |
| View Appointments | `AppointmentsListView()` | Tab: `.appointments` | None |
| Create Project | `CreateProjectSelectionView()` | Tab: `.createProject` | None |
| Project Details | `ProjectStatusTimelineView(projectId: String, isServiceProvider: Bool)` | NavigationLink | `projectId`, `isServiceProvider` |
| Service Providers | `ServiceProvidersView(selectedService: ServiceCategory)` | NavigationLink | `selectedService` |
| All Services | `PickServiceView()` | NavigationLink | None |
| Technician Profile | `TechUserProfileView(technicianId: Int)` | NavigationLink | `technicianId` |
| Chat List | `ChatsModule.ListView()` | NavigationLink | None |
| Notifications | `NotificationsView()` | NavigationLink | None |
| Portfolio | `PortfolioManagementView()` | NavigationLink | None |
| Create Portfolio | `CreatePortfolioView()` | Sheet | None |
| Available Projects (Tech) | `AvailableProjectsView()` | Tab: `.projects` | None |
| My Offers (Tech) | `MyOffersPage()` | NavigationLink | None |
| Payments (Tech) | `CommissionPaymentView()` | Tab: `.payments` | None |

