## üó∫Ô∏è Navigation Intent Mapping

### How to Use This Section
When a user asks "How do I...", match their intent to the navigation path below.

### Intent Categories

#### 1. Project Management
- **"I want to create a project"** 
  - Navigate to: `CreateProjectSelectionView()` 
  - Method: Select tab `.createProject` OR tap "+" button
  - View Component: `CreateProjectSelectionView()`

- **"I want to view my projects"** 
  - Navigate to: `AllUserProjectsView()`
  - Method: Select tab `.myProjects`
  - View Component: `AllUserProjectsView()`

- **"I want to see project status"** 
  - Navigate to: `ProjectStatusTimelineView(projectId: String, isServiceProvider: false)`
  - Method: NavigationLink from project card
  - View Component: `ProjectStatusTimelineView`
  - Parameters: `projectId` (required), `isServiceProvider: false`

- **"I want to edit my project"** 
  - Navigate to: `ProjectOwnerEditView()` (from ProjectStatusTimelineView)
  - Method: Tap "Edit" button in ProjectStatusTimelineView
  - View Component: `ProjectOwnerEditView()`

- **"I want to approve phases"** 
  - Navigate to: `PhaseApprovalView()` (from ProjectStatusTimelineView)
  - Method: Tap "Approve Phases" in ProjectStatusTimelineView
  - View Component: `PhaseApprovalView()`

- **"I want to sign contract"** 
  - Navigate to: Contract section in `ProjectStatusTimelineView`
  - Method: Tap "Sign Contract" button
  - View Component: Embedded in `ProjectStatusTimelineView`

#### 2. Service Provider Discovery
- **"I want to find a service provider"** 
  - Navigate to: `ServiceProvidersView(selectedService: serviceCategory)`
  - Method: Tap service card in HomeView
  - View Component: `ServiceProvidersView`
  - Parameters: `selectedService` (ServiceCategory)

- **"I want to see all services"** 
  - Navigate to: `PickServiceView()`
  - Method: Tap "All services" button in HomeView
  - View Component: `PickServiceView()`

- **"I want to search for services"** 
  - Navigate to: Search results in `HomeView`
  - Method: Use search bar at top of HomeView
  - View Component: `FloatingSearchResultsView` (embedded in HomeView)

- **"I want to book an appointment"** 
  - Navigate to: `TechUserProfileView(technicianId: Int)` ‚Üí Book Appointment
  - Method: Tap service provider ‚Üí Tap "Book Appointment"
  - View Component: `TechUserProfileView`
  - Parameters: `technicianId` (Int)

#### 3. Bidding & Offers (Service Providers)
- **"I want to bid on a project"** 
  - Navigate to: `ProjectStatusTimelineView(projectId: String, isServiceProvider: true)` ‚Üí Bid Form
  - Method: Projects tab ‚Üí Tap project ‚Üí "Bid Now" button
  - View Component: `ProjectStatusTimelineView` with `isServiceProvider: true`
  - Parameters: `projectId` (String), `isServiceProvider: true`

- **"I want to see available projects"** 
  - Navigate to: `AvailableProjectsView()`
  - Method: Select tab `.projects` (bottom left)
  - View Component: `AvailableProjectsView()`

- **"I want to view my bids"** 
  - Navigate to: `MyOffersPage()`
  - Method: Home tab ‚Üí "My Offers" button OR Projects tab ‚Üí "My Offers"
  - View Component: `MyOffersPage()`

- **"I want to see assigned projects"** 
  - Navigate to: `HomeContentView` ‚Üí Assigned Projects section
  - Method: Home tab (service provider)
  - View Component: Embedded in `HomeContentView`

#### 4. Portfolio Management (Service Providers)
- **"I want to create portfolio"** 
  - Navigate to: `CreatePortfolioView()`
  - Method: Home tab ‚Üí "Create Portfolio" button (purple)
  - View Component: `CreatePortfolioView()`

- **"I want to manage portfolio"** 
  - Navigate to: `PortfolioManagementView()`
  - Method: Profile tab ‚Üí My Portfolio card
  - View Component: `PortfolioManagementView()`

- **"I want to add past projects"** 
  - Navigate to: `AddPastProjectView()`
  - Method: Profile ‚Üí My Portfolio ‚Üí Past Projects ‚Üí "Add" button
  - View Component: `AddPastProjectView()`

#### 5. Appointments
- **"I want to view appointments"** 
  - Navigate to: `AppointmentsListView()`
  - Method: Select tab `.appointments` (bottom right)
  - View Component: `AppointmentsListView()`

- **"I want to book appointment"** 
  - Navigate to: `TechUserProfileView(technicianId: Int)` ‚Üí Book Appointment
  - Method: Service provider profile ‚Üí "Book Appointment" button
  - View Component: `TechUserProfileView`
  - Parameters: `technicianId` (Int)

- **"I want to reschedule"** 
  - Navigate to: `AppointmentsListView()` ‚Üí Tap appointment ‚Üí Reschedule
  - Method: Appointments tab ‚Üí Tap appointment card
  - View Component: Reschedule functionality in `AppointmentsListView()`

#### 6. Settings & Profile
- **"I want to change language"** 
  - Navigate to: `ProfileView()` ‚Üí Settings ‚Üí Language toggle
  - Method: Profile tab ‚Üí Settings section
  - View Component: Language toggle in `ProfileView()`

- **"I want to change font size"** 
  - Navigate to: `ProfileView()` ‚Üí Settings ‚Üí Font Size menu
  - Method: Profile tab ‚Üí Settings ‚Üí Font Size
  - View Component: Font size menu in `ProfileView()`

- **"I want to toggle dark mode"** 
  - Navigate to: `ProfileView()` ‚Üí Settings ‚Üí Dark Mode toggle
  - Method: Profile tab ‚Üí Settings ‚Üí Dark Mode
  - View Component: Dark mode toggle in `ProfileView()`

- **"I want to edit my profile"** 
  - Navigate to: `MyProfileView()` (for users) OR `TechnicianProfileManagementView()` (for technicians)
  - Method: Profile tab ‚Üí My Info card ‚Üí Tap
  - View Component: `MyProfileView()` or `TechnicianProfileManagementView()`

- **"I want to logout"** 
  - Navigate to: Logout action in `ProfileView()`
  - Method: Profile tab ‚Üí Scroll down ‚Üí Logout button
  - View Component: Logout button in `ProfileView()`

#### 7. Payments & Contracts
- **"I want to make payment"** 
  - Navigate to: `ContractPaymentView()` (from ProjectStatusTimelineView)
  - Method: My Projects ‚Üí Tap project ‚Üí Phase ‚Üí "Pay" button
  - View Component: `ContractPaymentView()`

- **"I want to view contract"** 
  - Navigate to: Contract section in `ProjectStatusTimelineView`
  - Method: My Projects ‚Üí Tap project ‚Üí Contract section
  - View Component: Contract viewer in `ProjectStatusTimelineView`

- **"I want to download contract PDF"** 
  - Navigate to: Contract section in `ProjectStatusTimelineView` ‚Üí Download
  - Method: My Projects ‚Üí Tap project ‚Üí Contract ‚Üí "Download PDF"
  - View Component: PDF download in `ProjectStatusTimelineView`

#### 8. Communication
- **"I want to chat"** 
  - Navigate to: `ChatsModule.ListView()`
  - Method: Header ‚Üí Chat icon (top right) OR Service provider profile ‚Üí Chat
  - View Component: `ChatsModule.ListView()`

- **"I want to see notifications"** 
  - Navigate to: `NotificationsView()`
  - Method: Header ‚Üí Bell icon (top right)
  - View Component: `NotificationsView()`

- **"I want help"** 
  - Navigate to: `ChatbotView()` (floating button)
  - Method: Home tab ‚Üí Floating chatbot button (bottom right)
  - View Component: `ChatbotView()`

