### Bidding on Projects

**Navigation Path:**
```
Projects tab OR Home tab ‚Üí Available Projects ‚Üí Tap project ‚Üí "Bid Now" button
```

**View Components:**
- Available Projects: `AvailableProjectsView()` (set `selectedTab = .projects`)
- Project Details: `ProjectStatusTimelineView(projectId: String, isServiceProvider: true)`
- Bid Form: `BidForm` (sheet or embedded in ProjectStatusTimelineView)

**Step-by-Step Instructions:**

1. **Find Available Projects**
   - **Method 1**: Tap "Projects" tab (bottom left)
   - **Method 2**: Home tab ‚Üí Scroll to "Available Projects" section
   - **Method 3**: Home tab ‚Üí "Look for Offers" button

2. **Browse Projects**
   - Projects displayed in 2-column grid
   - Each card shows:
     - Project title
     - Category/service type
     - Budget range
     - Status
     - Distance (if location enabled)
   - Scroll to see more projects

3. **Filter Projects** (optional)
   - Use filter options:
     - By category/service
     - By status
     - By location/distance
   - Tap filters to narrow results

4. **View Project Details**
   - Tap project card
   - See full project information:
     - Detailed description
     - All phases and requirements
     - Budget breakdown
     - Location/address
     - Project owner info

5. **Submit Bid**
   - Tap "Bid Now" button
   - Bid form opens
   - Fill required fields:
     - **Price per Phase**: Enter price for each phase
     - **Total Price**: Overall project price
     - **Estimated Duration**: How long project will take
     - **Notes**: Add comments, approach, materials (optional)
   - Review bid details
   - Tap "Submit Bid"

6. **After Submission**
   - Bid status: "Pending"
   - Project owner notified
   - Can view bid in "My Offers"
   - Wait for acceptance/rejection

7. **Bid Status**
   - **Pending**: Waiting for review
   - **Accepted**: Project assigned to you
   - **Rejected**: Not selected (no notification typically)

**Common Questions:**
- **"Can I edit my bid?"** ‚Üí No, but you can contact project owner via chat
- **"How many bids can I submit?"** ‚Üí One bid per project
- **"When will I know if accepted?"** ‚Üí Project owner will accept when ready, you'll be notified

---

### Managing Assigned Projects

**Navigation Path:**
```
Home tab ‚Üí "Assigned Projects" section
```

**View Components:**
- Home View: `HomeContentView(geo: geo)` (service provider)
- Assigned Projects: Embedded list in `HomeContentView`
- Project Details: `ProjectStatusTimelineView(projectId: String, isServiceProvider: true)`

**Step-by-Step Instructions:**

1. **View Assigned Projects**
   - Open Home tab
   - Scroll to "Assigned Projects" section
   - See list of projects assigned to you
   - Projects you've won bids on

2. **Project Status**
   - Each project shows:
     - Project title
     - Status (Approved, Contract, Active, etc.)
     - Progress indicator
     - Next action needed

3. **View Project Details**
   - Tap project card
   - See:
     - Full project description
     - All phases
     - Contract status
     - Payment status
     - Timeline

4. **Complete Phases**
   - **Prerequisites**:
     - Phase must be paid by project owner
     - Check phase status shows "Paid"
   - **Steps**:
     - Complete work for the phase
     - Tap "Complete Phase" button (only visible if paid)
     - Confirm completion
     - Phase status ‚Üí "Completed"
     - Next phase can begin

5. **Request Visit Appointment**
   - If site visit needed:
     - Tap "Request Visit" button
     - Select date and time
     - Add notes
     - Submit request
     - Project owner receives notification

6. **Upload Progress Photos**
   - In project view, find "Photos" section
   - Tap "Add Photo"
   - Select from gallery or take photo
   - Add caption (optional)
   - Upload
   - Photos visible to project owner

7. **View Payments**
   - Check "Payments" section
   - See which phases are paid
   - View payment history
   - Commission payments shown separately

**Common Questions:**
- **"Why can't I complete phase?"** ‚Üí Phase must be paid first, check payment status
- **"How do I contact project owner?"** ‚Üí Tap project ‚Üí Contact or Chat button
- **"When do I get paid?"** ‚Üí Commission payments shown in Payments tab

